        <span class="attribution__caption">Source: ProPublica review of <a href="https://globalizationandhealth.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s12992-021-00708-1">academic research</a>, World Trade Organization records, letters and other U.S. government documents, WikiLeaks cables and news accounts.</span>
    
