            </a>
        </div>
    
    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/utah-cleft-palate-team-says-approach-is-innovative-others-disagree">
                                    A Utah Cleft Palate Team Says Its Approach Is Innovative. Others See a Pattern of Unnecessary Surgeries on Children.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            At Primary Children’s Hospital in Utah, pediatric surgeons are taking controversial risks with how they care for kids with cleft lip and palate. Outside doctors found that some parents weren’t told their child’s care was different from the norm.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/megan-rose">Megan Rose</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-03-06EST05:00">March 6, 5 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    


                    
    
        <div class="lead-art">
            <a class="aspect-3-2" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/how-federal-government-fails-stop-syphilis-babies-pregnancy">
                <img
                    alt=""
                    src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%273%27%20height%3D%272%27%20style%3D%27background%3Atransparent%27%2F%3E"
                    srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/N0A9121.psd-OG_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=267&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=746aba6b0e3243eff5cb281fa47a6edf 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/N0A9121.psd-OG_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=533&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=8884ab6bb27b40874796cb3bd9621973 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/N0A9121.psd-OG_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=800&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=a8164a53a22591932de3625e2b59e6b0 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/N0A9121.psd-OG_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1067&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=0da4423e6a85c4ed0025ea5accfa6b82 1600w"
                    width="400"
                    height="267"
                    loading="lazy"
                    js-autosizes
                />
            </a>
        </div>
    
    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/how-federal-government-fails-stop-syphilis-babies-pregnancy">
                                    Syphilis Is Killing Babies. The U.S. Government Is Failing to Stop the Disease From Spreading.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            The only drug that treats syphilis during pregnancy is in short supply. Untreated, the disease can pass to newborns, killing them or leaving them with disabilities. As cases rise sharply, the government isn’t doing much to prevent shortages.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/anna-maria-barry-jester">Anna Maria Barry-Jester</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-03-04EST05:00">March 4, 5 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    
                <div class="lead-art">
            <a class="aspect-3-2" href="https://www.propublica.org/getinvolved/tell-us-about-mental-health-care-access">
                <img
                    alt=""
                    src="https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/getInvolved/_threeTwo400w/20240227-mental-health-callout-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg"
                    width="400"
                    height="267"
